## Phases

The project runs as **5 phases**, each driven by GSD's `/gsd:discuss-phase` → `/gsd:plan-phase` → `/gsd:execute-phase` → `/gsd:verify-work` → `/gsd:ship` loop.

| # | Name | CSDP step(s) | Outcome |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | elementary-facts | Step 1 (verbalize + populate) | Locked vocabulary + sample fact instances confirmed with the expert |
| 2 | fact-types | Steps 2–3 (draw + combine + derive) | YAML: candidate object types + binary fact types + populations |
| 3 | constraints | Steps 4–6 (uniqueness + mandatory + value + subtyping) | YAML extended with constraints; library + LLM proposals confirmed |
| 4 | verify | Step 7 (final review + modality labelling) | Verbalization shown; alethic/deontic labels applied; verifier runs |
| 5 | translate | Step 8 (PyRel emission) | Final `model.py` |

